(select initiativetopicagendatable.*, rbp.ID2 as bp_id, bpentity.Name as bp_name from Relationship rbp inner join Entity bpentity on rbp.ID2 = bpentity.ID inner join (select r.id1 as initiativetopic_id, e3.Name as initiativetopic_name, r.ID2 as agenda_id, e.Name as agenda_name, e.Type as agenda_type --r.id1,e3.Name, r.id2, e.name,e.class,e.type,r.relation,e.shortprops,e.Properties from relationship r inner join entity e on r.id2 = e.id inner join entity e3 on r.id1 = e3.id inner join ( select ID from Entity where type = 463 and Class = 3 ) initiativetopictable on initiativetopictable.ID = r.ID1 and e.name <> '' and e.Type NOT IN (456) ) initiativetopicagendatable on rbp.ID1 = initiativetopicagendatable.agenda_id
where bpentity.Type = 760 and bpentity.name <> '' and rbp.Relation = 15 ) bptable on rbr.ID1 = bptable.bp_id where brentity.Type = 436 and brentity.name <> '' order by bptable.initiativetopic_id, bptable.agenda_id, bptable.bp_id, rbr.ID1 asc

--e.class,e.type,r.relation,e.shortprops,e.Properties from relationship r inner join entity e on r.id2 = e.id inner join entity e3 on r.id1 = e3.id

and e.name <> '' and e.Type = 9 --and r.Relation = 14 order by process_id asc
